Read-only audit of all dsupdt update configurations in RDADB.
Reports every invalid dcupdt/dlupdt/drupdt record (non-fatal) and
exits 1 if any problem is found, 0 otherwise.

Run (scan all datasets):
    python3 -m rda_python_dsupdt._check_config

Run (limit to specific dataset IDs):
    python3 -m rda_python_dsupdt._check_config dNNNNNN [dNNNNNN ...]
